@node infowindow "Info del sample"
@{B}@{B}Info del sample@{UB}@{UU}

Info-tamańo:
rango	   inicio      fin   tamańo
visible @{">" link infoinput}@{"  12345" link inforead}@{">" link infoinput}@{"  12345" link inforead}@{">" link infoinput}@{"  12345" link inforead}
marcado @{">" link infoinput}@{"  12345" link inforead}@{">" link infoinput}@{"  12345" link inforead}@{">" link infoinput}@{"  12345" link inforead}
